{
  "stem": "1530.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 427.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 182,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because you know, he was on the trains a lot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 183,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe he was just afraid to show it--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 184,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--you know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 185,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sometimes--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 186,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--he did, and sometimes he didn't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 187,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because he went on this roller coaster of being a good son and then not wanting religion.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 187,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there were problems in my family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 188,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Totally rebellious.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 189,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, but I know that he went to-- he went to-- because my parents used to travel to Switzerland, because my father sold the Swiss wine.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 189,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took Phillip and they put him into a yeshiva in Montreux, Switzerland, which wasn't Hasidic, but it was religious.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 189,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, they put him even a fancier one in Hungary called Pap, in a town called Pap, P-A-P.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 189,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he did very well for a while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 189,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he always left it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 190,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 191,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know, but it was very famous and very good.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 192,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 193,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was-- my mother read every book.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 193,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had Freud's when it came out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 193,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had poetry in the house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 193,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had poetry readings in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 193,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother had friends who just came to talk to him-- to her about politics.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 193,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because she was very, very bright--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 194,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and good, and an exceptional person.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 195,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A chief rabbi.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 196,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were there for generations in Hajdunanas.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 197,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 197,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 198,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "H-A-J-D-U-N-A-N-A-S.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 199,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Chief rabbi.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 199,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But for generations they were.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 199,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then her brothers became-- and a very well-known family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 200,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Halperts, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 201,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I suppose so, but he was dead when I was born.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 202,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But my mother always said that his-- that her father was also a beautiful human being.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 202,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he couldn't take the First World War, and he died of heart failure.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 203,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
